Package: SpatialCoherence
Title: Comprehensive Spatial Ecotype Organization Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Ateeq", "Khaliq", email = "akhaliq@iu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Quantifies spatial organization patterns of multicellular ecotypes in spatial transcriptomics data. 
    Discovers which spatial environments form structured vs disorganized patterns using neighborhood-based algorithms.
    Provides user-defined classification thresholds and comprehensive analysis workflows.
